├─ CNBC RSS
└─ Bloomberg Terminal API (if available)

Trade Deals:
├─ Reuters Trade News
├─ BBC Business RSS
└─ Trade publications
```

**Processing Pipeline**:
```
1. Fetch from source
   ├─ RSS feed → Parse XML
   ├─ API → Get JSON
   └─ Web scraping → Extract HTML

2. Extract data
   ├─ Title
   ├─ Content
   ├─ Author
   ├─ Publish date
   ├─ Images
