4. Store in research database
   ├─ Save article
   ├─ Link to source
   ├─ Add metadata
   └─ Status: "research"
```

**Scheduling**:
```
Cron Jobs:
├─ Every 15 minutes: Breaking news sources
├─ Every 1 hour: Regular news sources
├─ Every 6 hours: Less frequent sources
└─ Daily: Weekly/monthly publications
```

